gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

God dwells there, saintly friends with Him, having done play and obtained great bliss;
Residing five nights at His place, then departed from there, getting enlightenment.

Here are the translations:

Aapyaa roopaiya muuthadi bhari, pachi tyaanthi padhariya Hari;
Aaviyaa luwangy salki gam, pachi prantiyee padhariya Shyama.
